Structs/Restaurant/CalendarTimeRange.htm.name: formatAsDates(dateFormat:dayFormat:)
Structs/Restaurant/CalendarTimeRange.htm.abstract: Format the properties of time range as date.

Extensions/Result.html#/s:s6ResultO21Che.name: isSuccess

Enums/ResponseError.html#/s:21CheetahDig.name: responseSerializationFailed(reason:)
Enums/ResponseError.html#/s:21CheetahDig.abstract: Returned when a response serializer throws an error in the serialization process.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: create(newUser:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Creates an Olo user. These are user accounts that have no associations with other login providers – i.e. the Olo user is the source of truth.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getOrCreate(userSSO:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Links a user from an authorized (OAuth) third party login provider to a new Olo user.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: createFromOrder(guid:password:optin:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Creates a new Olo user from the details provided in a previous guest order.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: authenticate(login:password:basketId:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Generates a new user authtoken and returns the user’s basic information.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: changePassword(oldPassword:newPassword:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Change an Olo user’s password.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: forgotPassword(email:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: The user matching the email address will be e-mailed a link to a page on the website where they can reset their password.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: revokeToken(completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Revokes the user authentication token

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getCurrentUser(completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns a User entity with their associated basic information

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: updateUser(updatedUser:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Updates the current user’s personal details

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: deleteAccount(completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Deletes the user account associated with the provided current Olo authentication token.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: checkUserExistence(email:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns a list of brand-supported login providers that have accounts with the user’s email address

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getContactDetails(completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns the user’s Contact Number.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: updateContactDetails(contactNumber:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Sets the user’s Contact Number in case of issues with orders.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getContactOptions(completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns the user’s current communication preferences, i.e. marketing email opt-in, upsell prompts, email receipts, and feedback follow-up.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: updateContactOptions(option:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Updates the user’s current communication preferences, i.e. marketing email opt-in, upsell prompts, email receipts, and feedback follow-up.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getDeliveryAddresses(completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns the user’s previously used delivery addresses.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: updateDefaultDeliveryAddress(addressId:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Sets the user’s default delivery address to the provided id.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: deleteDeliveryAddress(addressId:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Deletes the user’s address.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getBillingAccounts(basketId:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Lists all of the user’s billing accounts. Billing accounts are intended to be displayed on or near the checkout page.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: deleteBillingAccount(billingAccountId:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Removes a user’s billing account

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getGiftCardBalances(completion:)

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getFavorites(completion:)

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: deleteFavorite(favoriteId:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Removes a specific Favorite from the user’s account.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getFavoriteLocations(completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns a Favorite.UserFavoriteLocations for the user.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: addFavoriteLocation(locationId:isDefault:completion:)

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: deleteFavoriteLocation(locationId:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Removes a specific Favorite.Location from the user’s account.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getRecentOrders(completion:)

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getRecentOrders(reference:completion:)

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getOpenManualFireOrders(completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns a list of open Manual Fire orders that are waiting to be fired

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getQualifyingRewards(restaurantId:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns a list of qualifying rewards for the user

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getNearbyRewards(coordinates:radiusMiles:limit:completion:)

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getUser(byGuid:completion:)

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Updates the user’s personal details.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getContactDetails(byGuid:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns the user’s contact number.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: updateContactDetails(byGuid:contactNumber:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Sets the user’s Contact Number in case of issues with orders.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: getContactOptions(byGuid:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Returns the user’s current communication preferences, i.e. marketing email opt-in, upsell prompts, email receipts, and feedback follow-up.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: updateContactOptions(byGuid:option:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Updates the user’s current communication preferences, i.e. marketing email opt-in, upsell prompts, email receipts, and feedback follow-up.

Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.name: changePassword(byGuid:newPassword:completion:)
Enums/UserAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOl.abstract: Change an Olo user’s password.

Enums/RestaurantAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDig.name: getNearbyRestaurants(coordinates:calendarRange:radiusMiles:limit:completion:)

Enums/RestaurantAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDig.name: getRestaurants(byTelephone:completion:)
Enums/RestaurantAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDig.abstract: Returns a list of Public restaurants filtered by the restaurant phone number. Uses International 11-digit format, no spaces or punctuation (e.g. 15555555555)

Enums/RestaurantAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDig.name: getRestaurant(restaurantId:completion:)

Enums/RestaurantAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDig.abstract: Returns the absolute latest copy of a single restaurant’s menu as a list of categories and their products.

Enums/OrderAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalO.abstract: Returns an Order.Status entity about the order matching the calling system’s reference as passed into the submit method’s “orderref” argument.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: getBasket(_:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: updateGroupOrder(groupOrderId:deadline:note:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: createGroupOrder(restaurantId:basketId:deadline:note:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: sendGroupOrderInvites(groupOrderId:emailAddress:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: getGroupOrder(_:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: addProduct(_:toBasketId:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: addProductByChainId(_:toBasketId:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: addProducts(_:basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Add multiple products to basket.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: updateProducts(_:basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Modifies the existing products already in a basket.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: addProductsByChainId(_:basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Add multiple products by chain id to basket

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: addProductsByFave(id:basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Attempts to add all the products from a favorite (“fave”) into the specified basket.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: deleteCouponOrCompCode(basketId:promotionType:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Attempts to apply a coupon to the basket

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: applyCouponOrCompCode(code:toBasketId:promotionType:secondaryCode:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Attempts to apply a coupon to the basket

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: deleteCustomField(id:fromBasketId:completion:)

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: transferToAnotherRestaurant(basketId:restaurantId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Will attempt to transfer a basket to another restaurant (a.k.a. vendor), including all of that basket’s content and settings.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: transferToOloWebsite(basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Returns URLs to transfer an API basket to Olo’s whitelabel web (or mobile web) site, if such websites exist for the brand.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: getBillingSchemes(basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Returns all supported billing methods/schemes (e.g. credit card, pay in store [“cash”], or a gift card scheme) associated with the specified basket’s restaurant.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: getBillingScheme(id:basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Returns the billing method/scheme (e.g. credit card, pay in store [cash], or a gift card scheme) associated with the scheme id at the specified basket’s restaurant.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: getGiftCardBalance(billingSchemeId:cardNumber:pin:basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Returns the balance remaining on a specified gift card.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: getVerifyGiftCardPinRequirement(billingSchemeId:cardNumber:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Verify Gift Card PIN requirement.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: validate(basketId:checkUpsell:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Obtains final tax and total amounts from the associated restaurant’s Point of Sale (POS) system (when applicable) and completes a validation round-trip of the full basket and its contents.

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: submitOrderWithSinglePayment(order:basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Submit order with single payment

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: submitOrderWithMultiplePayments(order:basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Submit order with multiple payments

Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.name: requestCCSFPaymentToken(basketId:completion:)
Enums/BasketAPI.html#/s:21CheetahDigital.abstract: Use this endpoint to generate a GUID token that will be used to identify your transaction request when submitting an order through the Credit Card Submission Frame (CCSF). Using this approach will act as a replacement for the normal bakset submission flow (see linked documentation above). This token will be short-lived (2 hours) and can only be used once when submitting a successful order. If an order fails to submit, the token can be reused until the order is successful or the token expires.

Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.name: session
Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.abstract: The URLSession object used by the API to execute requests.

Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.name: resetSession()
Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.abstract: Resets the session by cancelling current tasks and invalidating current session and then creates a new session.

Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.name: getAccessToken()
Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.abstract: Gets the access token of the user of the current session.

Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.name: setCredentials(_:)
Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.abstract: Saves the credentials of the user of the current session.

Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.name: deleteCredentials()
Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.abstract: Deletes the current user session’s saved credentials.

Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.name: send(_:modelKeyPath:completion:)
Classes/API.html#/s:21CheetahDigitalOloC.abstract: Sends a request to the API using the current session.
